ately, we haven't been able to spend much time together at all."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[98]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I happily nodded at the rare invite, without any hesitation."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Not like I've got much else going on anyway."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[96]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\se[24-nb]\\SM[jump]\\SA[124]Yay, fufuh--... I can't wait~"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\SE[54-nb]Hey, \\n[1]. Am I... uhm."]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Do you think I'm a normal girl?"]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[98]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["A normal girl, huh... not really, she's so much more excellent than "]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["most girls in so many ways that I don't know how to really say it."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["[You are but... you're more amazing than normal, really.] is what I"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["went with, and she appeared to look relieved."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[96]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\SM[slidef]\\SE[21]Eheheh..."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[98]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["...I took her outstretched hand briskly, and we headed home"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["together, as my hopes for that day started building up on their own."]},{"code":121,"indent":0,"parameters":[409,409,0]},{"code":357,"indent":0,"parameters":["TRP_SkitMZ","end","スキット終了",{"noAnimation":"false"}]},{"code":657,"indent":0,"